---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Niche Systems Consulting">
    <main style="padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: left;">Our Philosophy</h1>

        <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        <div style="line-height: 1.8; color: #333; font-size: 1.1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem;">
                <p>
              
                We started this firm with the goal of tackling interdisciplinary challenges at the intersection of software and physical sciences while remaining deeply committed to our roots in <strong>software engineering</strong>. Whether we are automating data collection for a research department, building full-stack applications, custom 3D tools, distributed systems or anything else, our standard of precision remains the same.
              </p></div>
            </section>
        
        <!-- <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                The Principal-Led Model
            </h2>

        </section> -->

        <section style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                Our Capabilities
            </h2>
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
                <div style="padding: 2rem; border-left: 2px solid #111; background: #fafafa;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 0; color: #111;">Foundational Software</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">
                        <br />
                        Whether our clients need custom computation tools, graphical simulations, web applications or any other specialized software, we specialize in writing code that is fast, robust and secure. We solve problems with whichever languages and frameworks are best suited to the task, but we have a particular affinity for certain technologies (see our design philosophy).
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div style="padding: 2rem; border-left: 2px solid #0066cc; background: #f0f7ff;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 0; color: #111;">Domain Integration</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">
                        <br />
                        For projects requiring more than just code, we activate our <strong>Strategic Advisory</strong> team. We integrate experts in engineering and the sciences to help us guarantee that the software we are building correctly integrates into the physical world and addresses the unique challenges of our clients' domains.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
                <div style="padding: 2rem; border-left: 2px solid #111; background: #fafafa;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 0; color: #111;">Academic Research</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">
                        <br />
                        We have worked with several university research departments to build software that accelerates scientific discovery. We understand the unique challenges of academic research and are adept at building tools that integrate with existing workflows and data sources. We specialize in turning messy, manual workflows into streamlined, type-safe digital assets.
                </div>
                <div style="padding: 2rem; border-left: 2px solid #0066cc; background: #f0f7ff;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 0; color: #111;">Speed & Security</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">
                        <br />
                        Rather than go with the quickest or easiest solution, we prioritize building software that is robust (fast and secure). One way we achieve this is by using languages and frameworks that provide strong guarantees about code correctness and security, such as Rust. Rust, being a low-level language, allows us to optimize for performance as well, making it an ideal choice for many engineering applications.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                Why Niche Systems?
            </h2>
                        <div style="line-height: 1.8; color: #333; font-size: 1.1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem;">
                <p>
                    Niche Systems operates on a principal-led model where every engagement is spearheaded by our founder. This ensures that your project benefits from a single, high-accountability point of contact with deep software engineering expertise.
                </p>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div style="line-height: 1.8; color: #444; font-size: 1rem;">
                <p>
                    We don't believe in over-engineering simple solutions, nor do we shy away from high-complexity hurdles. Our firm is designed to provide the lean efficiency of a solo consultant for foundational projects, with the technical depth of a full engineering firm when the mission demands it.
                </p>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div style="line-height: 1.8; color: #444; font-size: 1rem;">
                <p>
                    With that being said, our team is still quite small, so project scope must be carefully defined to ensure that we can deliver the highest quality work on time and within budget. We're always happy to discuss potential projects and help prospective clients determine if we're the right fit for their needs.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>